ChartKit-package         ChartKit: Publication-Ready Data Visualization for R

Package Overview
ChartKit                ChartKit package documentation
print_chart_catalog     View all 48 available chart types
get_chart_catalog       Get chart catalog as data frame

Themes and Styling
theme_publication       Publication-ready theme (with grid)
theme_minimal_pub       Minimalist theme (no grid)
theme_classic_pub       Classic theme (strong borders)
scale_color_publication Colorblind-friendly color scale
scale_fill_publication  Colorblind-friendly fill scale
save_publication        Save high-quality figures for journals

Basic Charts (16 types)
viz_scatter             Scatter plot for relationships
viz_line                Line plot for time series
viz_bar                 Bar chart for categorical comparisons
viz_histogram           Histogram for distributions
viz_boxplot             Box plot for distribution and outliers
viz_violin              Violin plot for distribution shape
viz_density             Density plot for smooth distributions
viz_pie                 Pie chart for proportions
viz_donut               Donut chart with hollow center
viz_area                Area plot for cumulative data
viz_ribbon              Ribbon plot for confidence intervals
viz_step                Step plot for discrete changes
viz_errorbar            Error bar plot for uncertainty
viz_jitter              Jitter plot for categorical scatter
viz_qq                  Q-Q plot for distribution comparison
viz_ecdf                Empirical cumulative distribution

Intermediate Charts (15 types)
viz_heatmap             Heatmap for matrix visualization
viz_correlation         Correlation matrix heatmap
viz_contour             Contour plot for 3D surfaces
viz_density2d           2D density plot for bivariate data
viz_ridgeline           Ridgeline plot for distribution comparison
viz_waterfall           Waterfall chart for cumulative effects
viz_funnel              Funnel chart for conversion stages
viz_radar               Radar chart for multivariate comparison
viz_bubble              Bubble chart for three variables
viz_lollipop            Lollipop chart for ranked values
viz_dumbbell            Dumbbell chart for before/after
viz_cleveland_dot       Cleveland dot plot for comparisons
viz_violin_box          Combined violin and box plot
viz_raincloud           Raincloud plot (violin + box + points)
viz_polar_bar           Polar bar chart for circular data

Advanced Charts (17 types)
viz_sankey              Sankey diagram for flow visualization
viz_treemap             Treemap for hierarchical data
viz_sunburst            Sunburst chart for hierarchical proportions
viz_network             Network graph for relationships
viz_parallel            Parallel coordinates for multivariate analysis
viz_chord               Chord diagram for inter-relationships
viz_calendar_heatmap    Calendar heatmap for temporal patterns
viz_hexbin              Hexbin plot for large datasets
viz_stream              Stream graph for stacked time series
viz_alluvial            Alluvial diagram for categorical flows
viz_circular_bar        Circular bar chart for cyclical patterns
viz_bullet              Bullet chart for KPIs
viz_slope               Slope chart for two-point comparison
viz_wind_rose           Wind rose for directional data
viz_gantt               Gantt chart for project timelines
viz_mosaic              Mosaic plot for categorical associations
viz_marimekko           Marimekko chart for market share

Example Files
basic_examples.R            Basic chart types with proper data preparation
distribution_examples.R     30+ distribution visualization examples
scatter_advanced_examples.R Interactive scatter plots and correlations
categorical_examples.R      40+ bar plot variations with styling
circular_examples.R         Radar, circular bar, wind rose diagrams
specialized_examples.R      Lollipop, treemap, wordcloud examples
intermediate_examples.R     Heatmaps, bubble charts, waterfalls
advanced_examples.R         Sankey, network, chord diagram examples
